parent1.code: A sketch of five brass clockwork robots in the style of steampunk fantasy. They dance gracefully on the surface of a giant pocket watch floating in a swirling vortex of cosmic dust in the depths of space on a starry night, their gears clicking rhythmically, surrounded by constellations and nebulae that pulse with ethereal light.

offspring.code: A whimsical sketch of five gleaming brass clockwork robots with intricate gears in the style of Victorian steampunk fantasy. They pirouette gracefully on the ornate surface of a colossal antique pocket watch floating serenely in the infinite depths of space on a crisp starry night, their delicate gears clicking rhythmically in perfect synchronization, surrounded by twinkling constellations and swirling, iridescent nebulae.
